name: 伊桑·J·格林
name_full: 伊桑·J·格林 Ethan J Green
introduction: Ethan Green is an up-and-coming actor making his Netflix debut as a season regular on Stranger Things (2016) season 4 and in the upcoming series Echo 3 (2022) on Apple TV. Born in Daytona Beach (FL), is an identical twin to Oliver J Green, to a Czech mother and an American father. At age 4 was cast, together with his identical twin brother Oliver, as "Jack" in their first movie role in My Husband's Secret Wife (2018). Ethan & Oliver Green also have an older brother, Elijah Green (b. 2010), who will appear in a lead role as "Sam" in the movie Space Pups (2023).
